#### Alternative derivation for Total Time of Flight, T

Considering the whole motion, when the projectile has reached the ground, \(y\,=\,0\)

Taking the upward direction as positive, \(a_{y}\,=\,-\,g\), \(u_{y}\,=\,u\,\sin\!\theta\)

Using \(s_{y}\,\,=\,u_{y}\,t\,+\,\nicefrac{{1}}{{2}}\,a_{y}\,t^{2}\)

